'''Dr. Mitchell''' is part of the panel who interviewed [[April Kepner]] for a job.

==History==
Dr. Mitchell and two other doctors interview April Kepner for a job. They all seemed shocked at how extensive her resumé was. He later told [[Owen Hunt|Owen]] that he didn't believe that April was a good match for their hospital, personality-wise.

==Career==
Dr. Mitchell is an [[Attending|attending]] [[Surgery|surgeon]] at Northwestern Memorial Hospital.
